    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Honest driver-quality car that\u2019s ready to be enjoyed as-is and offers a nice entry point into ownership without stretching into premium territory. It presents well enough to be proud of, while showing the expected cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections of a fair-condition example. A solid, usable car with plenty to like for someone who values enjoyment and affordability over perfection.",
