    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Honest project car in poor condition that will need significant work before it can be relied on as a regular driver. It shows heavy age and wear throughout, with tired paint, worn trim, and an interior that looks used and in need of refurbishment. Expect deferred maintenance, cosmetic issues, and likely mechanical sorting before it is truly road-ready. Best suited for a hands-on buyer looking for a restoration candidate or budget project rather than a turn-key car.",
