    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, dependable transportation for the buyer who values value over flash. This vehicle is being offered as a budget-friendly option with visible wear consistent with age and use, making it a practical choice for commuting, a first car, or a project. A solid opportunity to get into a vehicle at a very accessible price point.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly car that could make a great runaround, first car, or tidy little project for someone handy. It\u2019s priced to reflect its age and condition, and for the right buyer it offers a lot of value without breaking the bank. If you want something honest, usable, and easy on the wallet, come have a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget driver with good bones and a strong-running powertrain. Starts up, shifts out, and tracks down the road with the kind of mechanical honesty that makes it a great commuter, first car, or weekend project. Cosmetic wear is present and it\u2019s not a showpiece, but the engine pulls well, the chassis feels planted, and it offers dependable, usable transportation with plenty of life left for the next owner willing to tidy it up. A straightforward, affordable car for someone who values function over flash.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Honest poor-condition sale with solid value for the money. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of worn-in personality you can\u2019t fake\u2014an honest, road-weathered machine with stories in every panel and plenty of life left for the right next chapter. It\u2019s the sort of ride that appeals to someone who sees charm where others see age: a great candidate for a budget-friendly daily, a hands-on project, or simply dependable transportation with unmistakable character. If you want something inexpensive, distinctive, and full of potential, this one is ready to be claimed.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
